🎮 Gamification Elements (must-have)

Pick 3–4 to keep it simple:

1. Points (XP)
2. Streaks (daily activity)
3. Badges (milestones)
4. Leaderboard (competition)
5. 📊 Progress Tracking

Show:

Total points
Completed quizzes
Accuracy %
Streak count



6. UI Screens You Should Design

At minimum:

Login Page
Dashboard
Quiz Page
Result Page
Leaderboard Page


9. Extra Features (if you want to stand out)
Timer for quizzes ⏱️
Sound effects 🎵
Daily challenges 📅
Levels (Level 1 → Level 2 unlock)
